{
  "stem": "3346.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't there when they were shot, but I had a-- she wasn't really adopted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was somebody-- she was-- a fr-- my mother's-- my mother's friend's daughter, and her mother was dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came to live with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't even-- that's another thing that I-- you see, Carol, I erased, by myself, an awful lot of things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can't get them back, like names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, she was killed in that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That, that was very unpleasant, this, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] because you see, at a certain time, if you had two children, you had to choose.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could keep only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made my mother choose, of course, between her and me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I suppose for my mother there was no choice, but she must have felt like a murderer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It wasn't the sort of thing that we were separated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We, we were on one side of the street, and the ones who were going to be shot were on the other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was this boy who offered one of the Germans a fountain pen to, to let him go, to let him live.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a boy I knew very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just-- those are just sort of little things I remember that I haven't been able to, to erase.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Sorry, but some things-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, we were taken to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All this bit from the-- from the time when they shot them, and they were lying there in, in the sun to, to how and when I got to Plaszow-- all that is out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not arriving there, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
